         The biggest issues I see with this:</P><P>1) Mage elemental pets are specialized to be immune to certain spells.  Might wanna make this change only to their epic and other non-elemental based pets being considered.</P><P>2) More and more high end encounters are starting to use Lure Based AEs for everything.  However, these changes will really help in Velious, Kunark, Old World, and parts of Luclin.</P><P>"Time is meaningless to one who lives forever."<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
